f'''\n   = { num } \033[92m+ { num * ( percentage / 100 ) } <~ (The Increase Value) \033[39m 
\n   â‰ˆ { num + ( num * ( percentage / 100 ) ) } '''  
##OR:- { num * ( 1 + ( percentage / 100 ) ) }  
